History
*******

   Here is a list of the versions:

   @{b}*@{ub}     @{i}Release 1@{ui} (Winarrange 0.67beta)

     Initial Aminet release. Available on AminetCD6 @{b}aminet/util/misc@{ub}.

   @{b}*@{ub}     @{i}Release 2@{ui} (WinArrange 0.68beta)

     Winarrange now accepts `Jokers' like: @{b}ACCEPTWINDOW This?*Joker@{ub}.
        Please consult the documentation for detailed information.

     Note: The @{b}ACCEPT/REJECTTASK@{ub} options do not work yet.


